module:
   development.folder="dvlp">


    module, individual, activity, relationship, structure, process plant













     This part of ISO 10303 specifies an application module to record:


the decomposition of an activity into component activities; 

the connections between activities;

the involvement of things in activities.







the existence of an individual activity;



a whole-part relationship between two individual activities;



a connection relationship between two individual activities;



an involvement of a thing in
an individual activity.







 class of activity;
Class of activity is within the scope of the
Class_of_activity_structure application
module. 



membership of a class of activity.
Membership of a class of activity is within the scope
of the Activity_structure_and_classification application module.
